## Summary
This documentation details the Google Analytics 4 (iOS/Android) streaming integration in Amplitude Activation, which forwards events and user data from Amplitude to GA4 for Firebase-instrumented mobile applications, requiring a Firebase App ID and Measurement Protocol API Secret for setup.

